{"tid":1706957,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"怎樣才算警察犯錯？","createTime":"2019-11-11T08:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T09:08:48.000Z","uid":42487,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0dd7089f039150704240bec6f091c89b929cdd","tid":1706957,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:02:58.000Z","msg":"1.要在速龍顛峰期定勝負<br />\n2.要在警隊內部沒有矛盾的時候出勤<br />\n3.要在謝sir狀態最好的時候開記招<br />\n4.你不能往封鎖線外罵警察<br />\n5.你不能用雷射筆<br />\n6.你不能自慰反擊，你要全隊都站立靜止<br />\n7.你不能將示威升級，要給警隊對於足夠的空間發揮<br />\n8.你不能擺路障<br />\n9.在示威區，你不能有主場哨，記者要偏向警隊，最好一開場就給記者話你暴徒<br />\n10.開記招時，你不能幾個記者去發問，要讓警察單方面順利進行<br />\n11.你不能串警察<br />\n12.你行動前要把警隊每個警員都通知過一遍，最好事前預約被捕，然後再行動升級，這樣才是真水平，否則藍絲認為是靠運氣<br />\n13.和理非在示威區不能出現<br />\n14.你要允許警隊有足夠休息和觀看記者的所有照片和影片<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心升級了，藍絲也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。藍絲總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該示威升級。"},{"pid":"6a426117bb9bbc9bbb4460988f5579b8669965f4","tid":1706957,"uid":135461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45348dbcb7bc2398a7656d8477dbd644b849f8c","tid":1706957,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242fb785f2e1f90eb9be3432c5604cd8e8bf6948","tid":1706957,"uid":218659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:10:03.000Z","msg":"Btw自衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585de8fd7400af2ce23ba576512544651500330f","tid":1706957,"uid":42487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"242fb785f2e1f90eb9be3432c5604cd8e8bf6948","tid":1706957,"uid":218659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:10:03.000Z","msg":"Btw自衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"sor 打個陣都覺得怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e304dd9d6a9608af1f07273533f90628c5f92047","tid":1706957,"uid":316048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:32:45.000Z","msg":"網傳解放軍清算前線?<br />\n客觀分析，其實未必冇可能<br />\n一石二鳥，一可以化解民怨，二可建立一個訊息比大家知，就係只係一直都只係前線胡作非為冇聽上頭指示，不失為中國為得香港民心之方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於解放軍點清算，可能有2個方法:<br />\n1. 混入前線，係執行職務時搜集證據，交由獨立委員會清算<br />\n2. 係前線下班後武力拘捕<br />\n<br />\n林鄭你諗諗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58f1e190a3c11d6fd9c90fb0325395694d7eb79","tid":1706957,"uid":138948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:39:06.000Z","msg":"死疤"},{"pid":"29db881b12dc7cdaa79249f8189ac0c649bb3845","tid":1706957,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"9.在示威區，你不能有主場哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be2a52748eeb95db364e2bb48240199aeb18bd5","tid":1706957,"uid":45158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:41:49.000Z","msg":"聖人都有錯， popo唔會錯"},{"pid":"dca82623c91d5794cfd4bfa7caf7bb056eab1e30","tid":1706957,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:42:40.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街好經典"},{"pid":"602ffecfe51f0344b48906adbeb84371f3e03563","tid":1706957,"uid":88937,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"班仆街做過既仆街事寫出黎厚撚過聖經"},{"pid":"349bcaf41c769b0546825fb02c88e908c6803c79","tid":1706957,"uid":7609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80